$ Partition the set {1..N} into two classes

letting n be 500

find class : matrix indexed by [int(1..n)] of int(1..2)
 
such that

and([(a**2 + b**2 = c**2) -> or([class[a] != class[b] ,class[b] != class[c], class[c] != class[a]]) | a: int(1..n), b: int(1..n), c: int(1..n)])
